                    <p>She created the Instants monument to commemorate the 70th anniversary of the Second World War on Utah Beach, the Causse tomb at the Montparnasse cemetery and the monumental installation Phares displayed on Place de la Concorde in Paris in 2015, on the occasion of the ‘international year of light’ initiated by Unesco. </p>
